==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: yŏu qián néng shĭ guĭ tuīmó
===Proverb===
'''[[有]][[錢]][[能]][[使]][[鬼]][[推磨]]'''
# If you have money, you can make the devil push the millstone for you; Money makes the world go around; Money talks.
